    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你能在这款精确平台跳跃/收集金币的游戏中挑战致命关卡，并获得高分吗？反转重力并跳跃，在充满危险的试炼中探索道路，收集金币和丰厚奖励。三种游戏模式可供选择。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不朽模式 - 探索 10 个关卡，撞到障碍物会损失三分之一的分数。贪婪前行，争取登上排行榜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无情模式 - 无尽模式，障碍物会减少生命值。贪得无厌的话，你的游戏会被提前终止。难度也会随着进度增加。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >极速模式 - 一场 4-5 分钟的竞速赛，拾取金币会加速，而跳跃会略微减速。争夺最快通关时间！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >获取奖励</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039650/extras/10fb58db119f718e8cd08c6c899d98db.poster.avif?t=1762961948\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039650/extras/10fb58db119f718e8cd08c6c899d98db.webm?t=1762961948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039650/extras/10fb58db119f718e8cd08c6c899d98db.mp4?t=1762961948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集金币来填充左侧的连击槽。填满后，你可以从 3 种奖励中选择一个，以增强本次游戏体验。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >极速通关</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039650/extras/db8075cd69d28a4d52d0c621ea752536.poster.avif?t=1762961948\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039650/extras/db8075cd69d28a4d52d0c621ea752536.webm?t=1762961948\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3039650/extras/db8075cd69d28a4d52d0c621ea752536.mp4?t=1762961948\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着收集金币，你会越来越快。尽可能频繁地使用重力切换，因为跳跃会减慢速度。撞到障碍物会让你的速度完全归零。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
